					              multiple sectors. Our commitment to excellence drives us to create
					              lasting value for our stakeholders and communities.
				</p>
				<button class="text-[#285F99] !mt-4 !px-4 w-[200px] !py-2 border-1 border-[#9D8055] font-medium hover:bg-blue-100 transition-all duration-300 rounded text-xl text-left">
					Read more
